profile: With professional, dedicated plumbing service to all major cities and surrounding areas in Alberta, and with some of the best plumbers in the industry, The Gentlemen Plumbers work hard to exceed your expectations and deliver quality. If you need a plumber, call us today for plumbing or heating issues, leaky sinks and faucets, clogged drains, toilet, bathtub and shower repairs, furnace cleaning and repairs, hot water tanks and tankless hot water heaters, furnace installation and maintenance, trenchless pipe repair, camera sewer inspection, and more! We have local branches in Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, and Medicine Hat, with extended service all over Southern Alberta, including Camrose, Sherwood Park, St. Albert, Airdrie, High River, Crossfield, Carstairs, Olds, Innisfail, Wetaskiwin, Leduc, Lacombe, Okotoks, Nanton, Taber, Cardston, Didsbury, Brooks, Crowsnest Pass, Cochrane, Strathmore, Sundre, Three Hills, Ponoka, Fort Macleod, Pincher Creek, Bowden, Fort Saskatchewan, Chestermere, Sylvan Lake, Spruce Grove, and Stony Plain.

profile:
Proline Electric Ltd. is a family owned and operated local business.  Our electricians are all highly trained, licensed, background checked and drug tested for your safety and peace of mind.  Our top priorities are customer service and safety.  You can trust Proline Electric in your home or place of business. Need an electrician call Proline Electric Ltd.! We are your Electrician!


We work on everything electrical in your home, whether itâ€™s a switch that doesn't work, or a breaker box that needs to be replaced; a light that you want hung, or new landscape lighting!

WE DO IT ALL!
100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEES
Why People Choose Proline Electric! Your Friendly Electrician!

We only hire the best Electricians; 
Our Electricians are Drug Tested, Background Checked and Licensed.  

Upfront Pricing: 
We will show you the exact price and get your approval before starting your electrical work.  In addition, we stand by our quoted price.  You'll never pay more.

Our Warehouse on Wheels:
We stock our trucks with thousands of parts so we can almost always finish the job immediately.

Our Promise:
100% Satisfaction Guarantee!
Our electricians are background checked and drug tested for your peace of mind.  If our electricians do not wear shoe covers, or leave your home without cleaning up after themselves, you do not pay for the service.


Schedule your FREE on site estimate today!
